HEADWORD: Lumpish
<hw>Lump"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a lump; inert; gross; heavy;
dull; spiritless.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧ <xex>Lumpish</xex>, heavy,
melancholy.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Lump"ish*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Lump"ish*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lumpsucker</ent>⟦br⟧
